Mr. Sign

T.H.E Dance Company draws from their archives In the series “Moving through COVID-19” and showcases resident choreographer Jae Duk Kim's creation, Mr. Sign. .
Kim Jae Duk’s “black swans” take us on a quest of self-realisation. For viewing from 23 May 2020 to 5 June 2020. Read synopsis at https://www.apart.sg/featured-season-7/thedanceco-mr-sign
